[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1060},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":1037,"related:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":1045},"\u002Fen\u002Fai\u002F2026\u002F03\u002F20\u002Fclaude-code-channels-instead-of-openclaw\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1015,"date":1016,"description":1017,"extension":1018,"lang":1019,"meta":1020,"navigation":1021,"path":1022,"readingMinutes":1023,"seo":1024,"standalone":1025,"stem":1026,"tags":1027,"tldr":1033,"updated":1034,"url":1035,"__hash__":1036},"content\u002Fai\u002F不想用龍蝦-OpenClaw-來試試看-Claude-Code-channels-吧！.md","不想用龍蝦（OpenClaw）？來試試看 Claude Code channels 吧！","2827818448",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1000},"minimark",[11,18,26,30,33,36,39,43,46,49,52,55,58,62,65,99,102,107,110,113,146,149,160,163,176,179,183,191,194,210,215,221,228,244,247,252,257,265,273,278,285,294,298,301,318,321,324,329,334,339,345,354,359,362,367,370,384,388,391,414,425,430,444,447,450,456,464,467,490,496,499,514,517,523,527,530,535,544,550,553,559,562,567,572,575,581,584,590,596,616,622,625,631,636,639,653,657,660,678,689,694,708,711,717,722,725,745,759,762,775,778,784,800,804,807,810,813,828,841,844,848,851,944,947,964,967,970,996],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":6,"src":17},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FGemini_Generated_Image_307jf3307jf3307j_1280x714.png",[19,20,23],"callout",{"title":21,"type":22},"Note","note",[12,24,25],{},"Claude Code channels 是 Anthropic 推出的官方解法，可以把外部事件（Telegram、Discord）推送進 Claude Code Session。跟第三方的龍蝦（OpenClaw）相比，channels 偏向「事件驅動」（推送 CI 結果、警報），龍蝦則是用聊天平台直接操控電腦。",[27,28,29],"h2",{"id":29},"前言",[12,31,32],{},"如果你有在關注 AI Agent 相關的工具，應該多少聽過龍蝦（OpenClaw）這個工具吧？簡單來講，龍蝦可以讓你透過聊天平台來遠端操控電腦上的 AI Agent，但其實 Claude Code 最近也推出了類似的功能，叫做「Channels」。",[12,34,35],{},"Channels 的概念跟龍蝦非常類似，都是讓你可以透過外部平台（像是 Telegram、Discord）來對正在運行的 Claude Code Session 發送訊息，讓 Claude 可以在背景幫你處理任務。不同的是，Channels 是 Anthropic 官方推出的功能，所以在穩定性和安全性上會更有保障，也不用擔心被判定為違規操作。",[12,37,38],{},"那這篇文章就來帶大家了解 Channels 是什麼、怎麼設定、以及實際上要怎麼使用吧。",[27,40,42],{"id":41},"claude-code-channels-是什麼","Claude Code Channels 是什麼？",[12,44,45],{},"簡單來講，Channel 其實就是一個 MCP Server，它可以把外部的事件（訊息、通知、Webhook 等）推送到你正在運行的 Claude Code Session 中，讓 Claude 能夠在你不在終端機前的時候，也能夠對這些事件做出反應。",[12,47,48],{},"而且 Channels 是雙向的——Claude 不只可以接收訊息，還可以透過同一個 Channel 回覆訊息。舉例來說，你在 Telegram 上傳一段訊息給 Bot，Claude 會在終端機中處理這個請求，然後把結果回傳到 Telegram 上，你就可以直接在手機上看到結果了。",[12,50,51],{},"這邊要注意的是，當 Claude 透過 Channel 回覆的時候，你在終端機上只會看到 inbound 的訊息和工具呼叫的確認（像是「sent」），實際的回覆內容會出現在另一個平台上（例如 Telegram 或 Discord）。",[12,53,54],{},"不過事件只有在 Session 開啟的時候才會到達，所以如果你想要 24 小時不間斷的接收訊息的話，你就需要讓 Claude Code 在背景程序或持久化的終端機中持續運行唷。",[12,56,57],{},"另外補充一下，Channels 目前還是 Research Preview 階段，需要 Claude Code v2.1.80 或以上版本，而且只支援 claude.ai 登入，不支援 Console 或 API Key 認證。如果你是 Team 或 Enterprise 方案的話，管理員需要先啟用才能使用。",[27,59,61],{"id":60},"開始之前要準備什麼","開始之前要準備什麼？",[12,63,64],{},"在開始設定之前，你需要先確認以下幾件事：",[66,67,68,77,84],"ul",{},[69,70,71,72,76],"li",{},"Claude Code v2.1.80 或以上版本（可以用 ",[73,74,75],"code",{},"claude --version"," 來確認）",[69,78,79,80,83],{},"claude.ai 帳號（需要透過 ",[73,81,82],{},"\u002Flogin"," 登入，不支援 API Key）",[69,85,86,87,94,95,98],{},"安裝 ",[88,89,93],"a",{"href":90,"rel":91},"https:\u002F\u002Fbun.sh",[92],"nofollow","Bun","（Channel Plugin 是用 Bun 來運行的，可以用 ",[73,96,97],{},"bun --version"," 來確認有沒有安裝）",[12,100,101],{},"這些東西如果沒有準備好的話，後面的步驟是沒辦法順利進行的唷。",[103,104,106],"h3",{"id":105},"安裝-bun","安裝 Bun",[12,108,109],{},"Channel Plugin 都是用 Bun 來跑的，所以這邊要先安裝一下。如果你已經有裝過的話可以跳過這一段。",[12,111,112],{},"macOS \u002F Linux \u002F WSL：",[114,115,120],"pre",{"className":116,"code":117,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","curl -fsSL https:\u002F\u002Fbun.sh\u002Finstall | bash\n","bash","",[73,121,122],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,124,127,131,135,139,143],"span",{"class":125,"line":126},"line",1,[123,128,130],{"class":129},"smYoP","curl",[123,132,134],{"class":133},"stw71"," -fsSL",[123,136,138],{"class":137},"sWayO"," https:\u002F\u002Fbun.sh\u002Finstall",[123,140,142],{"class":141},"sOudu"," |",[123,144,145],{"class":129}," bash\n",[12,147,148],{},"Windows PowerShell：",[114,150,154],{"className":151,"code":152,"language":153,"meta":119,"style":119},"language-powershell shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","powershell -c \"irm bun.sh\u002Finstall.ps1 | iex\"\n","powershell",[73,155,156],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,157,158],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,159,152],{},[12,161,162],{},"安裝完之後可以用以下指令來確認有沒有安裝成功：",[114,164,166],{"className":116,"code":165,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"bun --version\n",[73,167,168],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,169,170,173],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,171,172],{"class":129},"bun",[123,174,175],{"class":133}," --version\n",[12,177,178],{},"如果有正確跑出版本號的話就代表安裝成功囉～",[27,180,182],{"id":181},"先用-fakechat-來體驗看看","先用 fakechat 來體驗看看",[12,184,185,186,190],{},"在正式設定 Telegram 或 Discord 之前，我們可以先用官方提供的 ",[187,188,189],"strong",{},"fakechat"," 來體驗一下 Channels 的運作方式。fakechat 是一個在 localhost 上運行的聊天 UI，不需要任何外部服務或認證，非常適合拿來測試。",[12,192,193],{},"首先啟動一個 Claude Code Session，然後輸入以下指令來安裝 fakechat Plugin：",[114,195,197],{"className":116,"code":196,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"\u002Fplugin install fakechat@claude-plugins-official\n",[73,198,199],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,200,201,204,207],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,202,203],{"class":129},"\u002Fplugin",[123,205,206],{"class":137}," install",[123,208,209],{"class":137}," fakechat@claude-plugins-official\n",[19,211,212],{"title":21,"type":22},[12,213,214],{},"輸入之後，請記得重啟 Claude Code，讓 Plugin 被正確載入，否則後續的設定指令可能會找不到唷。",[12,216,217],{},[15,218],{"alt":219,"src":220},"安裝畫面","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320144433.png",[12,222,223,224,227],{},"安裝完成之後，先退出 Claude Code，然後用 ",[73,225,226],{},"--channels"," 參數重新啟動：",[114,229,231],{"className":116,"code":230,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"claude --channels plugin:fakechat@claude-plugins-official\n",[73,232,233],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,234,235,238,241],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,236,237],{"class":129},"claude",[123,239,240],{"class":133}," --channels",[123,242,243],{"class":137}," plugin:fakechat@claude-plugins-official\n",[12,245,246],{},"這樣 fakechat 的伺服器就會自動啟動了。",[12,248,249],{},[15,250],{"alt":189,"src":251},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320145628.png",[12,253,254],{},[15,255],{"alt":189,"src":256},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320145653.png",[12,258,259,260,264],{},"接著打開瀏覽器，前往 ",[88,261,262],{"href":262,"rel":263},"http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:8787",[92],"，你會看到一個簡單的聊天介面，試著輸入一段訊息，例如：",[114,266,271],{"className":267,"code":269,"language":270,"meta":119},[268],"language-text","哈囉你好\n","text",[73,272,269],{"__ignoreMap":119},[12,274,275],{},[15,276],{"alt":189,"src":277},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320145339.png",[12,279,280,281,284],{},"這時候訊息就會被推送到你的 Claude Code Session 中，Claude 會讀取訊息並處理，然後透過 fakechat 的 ",[73,282,283],{},"reply"," 工具把結果回傳到聊天介面上，你就可以直接在瀏覽器上看到結果囉～",[19,286,287],{"title":21,"type":22},[12,288,289,290,293],{},"如果 Claude 在執行過程中遇到權限提示，Session 會暫停直到你在終端機上手動核准。如果你想要完全無人值守的話，可以用 ",[73,291,292],{},"--dangerously-skip-permissions"," 來跳過權限提示，但請只在你信任的環境中使用唷。",[27,295,297],{"id":296},"設定-telegram-channel","設定 Telegram Channel",[12,299,300],{},"體驗完 fakechat 之後，接下來我們就來設定真正的 Telegram Channel 吧！",[12,302,303,304,309,310,313,314,317],{},"首先打開 Telegram，搜尋 ",[88,305,308],{"href":306,"rel":307},"https:\u002F\u002Ft.me\u002FBotFather",[92],"BotFather"," 並發送 ",[73,311,312],{},"\u002Fnewbot","，接著依照指示給你的 Bot 設定一個顯示名稱和一個以 ",[73,315,316],{},"bot"," 結尾的使用者名稱。設定完成後，BotFather 會回傳一組 Token，把它複製起來。",[12,319,320],{},"但為了確保大家順利，這邊還是寫了一下步驟：",[12,322,323],{},"搜尋 @BotFather 並建立新 Bot，剛進去會看到這樣的畫面：",[12,325,326],{},[15,327],{"alt":308,"src":328},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1609.jpg",[19,330,331],{"title":21,"type":22},[12,332,333],{},"請注意必須要有認證的藍勾勾的才是真的 BotFather 不是我底下打紅叉叉的假 BotFather 喔～",[12,335,336],{},[15,337],{"alt":308,"src":338},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1610.jpg",[12,340,341,342,344],{},"接著輸入 ",[73,343,312],{}," 來建立一個新的 Bot，BotFather 會先問你「Alright, a new bot. How are we going to call it? Please choose a name for your bot.」，意思是「你要替你的 Bot 取什麼名字呢？」這個名字可以隨便取，之後也可以改，所以不用太在意。",[12,346,347,348,350,351,353],{},"接著會問你「Good. Now let's choose a username for your bot. It must end in ",[73,349,316],{},".」，意思是「好，現在幫你的 Bot 選一個使用者名稱吧！必須要以 ",[73,352,316],{}," 結尾喔！」這個使用者名稱是 Telegram 上的唯一識別碼，不能跟其他 Bot 重複，所以可能需要試幾次才能找到一個可用的。",[12,355,356],{},[15,357],{"alt":308,"src":358},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1611.jpg",[12,360,361],{},"最後你就可以拿到 HTTP API Token 啦！它會是一串由英文字母、數字和冒號組成的長字串，請把它記下來（也請不要分享或者外流給他人）。",[12,363,364],{},[15,365],{"alt":308,"src":366},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1612.jpg",[12,368,369],{},"接著回到 Claude Code，輸入以下指令來安裝 Telegram Plugin：",[114,371,373],{"className":116,"code":372,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"\u002Fplugin install telegram@claude-plugins-official\n",[73,374,375],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,376,377,379,381],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,378,203],{"class":129},[123,380,206],{"class":137},[123,382,383],{"class":137}," telegram@claude-plugins-official\n",[19,385,386],{"title":21,"type":22},[12,387,214],{},[12,389,390],{},"安裝完之後，用剛剛從 BotFather 取得的 Token 來設定：",[114,392,394],{"className":116,"code":393,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"\u002Ftelegram:configure \u003Ctoken>\n",[73,395,396],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,397,398,401,404,407,411],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,399,400],{"class":129},"\u002Ftelegram:configure",[123,402,403],{"class":141}," \u003C",[123,405,406],{"class":137},"toke",[123,408,410],{"class":409},"s8XSl","n",[123,412,413],{"class":141},">\n",[12,415,416,417,420,421,424],{},"這會把 Token 儲存在專案的 ",[73,418,419],{},".claude\u002Fchannels\u002Ftelegram\u002F.env"," 中。當然你也可以在啟動 Claude Code 之前，先在 Shell 環境中設定 ",[73,422,423],{},"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN"," 環境變數，這樣就不用每次都跑 configure 了。",[12,426,427,428,227],{},"設定完之後，退出 Claude Code，然後帶上 ",[73,429,226],{},[114,431,433],{"className":116,"code":432,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"claude --channels plugin:telegram@claude-plugins-official\n",[73,434,435],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,436,437,439,441],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,438,237],{"class":129},[123,440,240],{"class":133},[123,442,443],{"class":137}," plugin:telegram@claude-plugins-official\n",[12,445,446],{},"這會啟動 Telegram Plugin，開始輪詢你的 Bot 的訊息。",[12,448,449],{},"接著打開 Telegram，對你的 Bot 發送任何一段訊息，Bot 就會回覆你一組配對碼。",[12,451,452],{},[15,453],{"alt":454,"src":455},"Telegram Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1613.jpg",[19,457,458],{"title":21,"type":22},[12,459,460,461,463],{},"如果你的 Bot 沒有回應，請確認 Claude Code 是不是有帶 ",[73,462,226],{}," 參數在運行中，因為 Bot 只有在 Channel 啟動的狀態下才能回覆唷。",[12,465,466],{},"拿到配對碼之後，回到 Claude Code 輸入：",[114,468,470],{"className":116,"code":469,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"\u002Ftelegram:access pair \u003Ccode>\n",[73,471,472],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,473,474,477,480,482,485,488],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,475,476],{"class":129},"\u002Ftelegram:access",[123,478,479],{"class":137}," pair",[123,481,403],{"class":141},[123,483,484],{"class":137},"cod",[123,486,487],{"class":409},"e",[123,489,413],{"class":141},[12,491,492],{},[15,493],{"alt":494,"src":495},"配對碼","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320151558.png",[12,497,498],{},"然後記得鎖定存取權限，確保只有你的帳號可以發送訊息：",[114,500,502],{"className":116,"code":501,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"\u002Ftelegram:access policy allowlist\n",[73,503,504],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,505,506,508,511],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,507,476],{"class":129},[123,509,510],{"class":137}," policy",[123,512,513],{"class":137}," allowlist\n",[12,515,516],{},"這樣就設定完成囉！你現在可以直接透過 Telegram 對 Claude Code 下指令了～",[12,518,519],{},[15,520],{"alt":521,"src":522},"下指令","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202026-03-20%2015.19.38.png",[27,524,526],{"id":525},"設定-discord-channel","設定 Discord Channel",[12,528,529],{},"如果你比較常用 Discord 的話，也可以選擇設定 Discord Channel，步驟跟 Telegram 類似，但多了一些 Discord 特有的設定。",[19,531,532],{"title":21,"type":22},[12,533,534],{},"小提醒一下，建議你先建立一個自己的 Discord 伺服器會比較好後續的操作。",[12,536,537,538,543],{},"首先前往 ",[88,539,542],{"href":540,"rel":541},"https:\u002F\u002Fdiscord.com\u002Fdevelopers\u002Fapplications",[92],"Discord Developer Portal","，點選「New Application」並設定名稱",[12,545,546],{},[15,547],{"alt":548,"src":549},"Discord Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152138.png",[12,551,552],{},"接著側邊欄找到「Bot」",[12,554,555],{},[15,556],{"alt":557,"src":558},"Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152312.png",[12,560,561],{},"然後點選「Reset Token」並複製 Token",[12,563,564],{},[15,565],{"alt":548,"src":566},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152222.png",[12,568,569],{},[15,570],{"alt":548,"src":571},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152247.png",[12,573,574],{},"接著在 Bot 的設定頁面中，往下滑到「Privileged Gateway Intents」，把「Message Content Intent」啟用，這個很重要，如果沒有啟用的話 Bot 是讀不到訊息內容的。",[12,576,577],{},[15,578],{"alt":579,"src":580},"Message Content Intent","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152531.png",[12,582,583],{},"接著側邊欄找到「OAuth2」",[12,585,586],{},[15,587],{"alt":588,"src":589},"OAuth2","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152634.png",[12,591,592,593,595],{},"然後前往「URL Generator」，勾選 ",[73,594,316],{}," 範圍，然後啟用以下權限：",[66,597,598,601,604,607,610,613],{},[69,599,600],{},"檢視頻道（View Channels）",[69,602,603],{},"發送訊息（Send Messages）",[69,605,606],{},"讀取訊息歷史（Read Message History）",[69,608,609],{},"在討論串中發送訊息（Send Messages in Threads）",[69,611,612],{},"附加檔案（Attach Files）",[69,614,615],{},"加入反應（Add Reactions）",[12,617,618],{},[15,619],{"alt":620,"src":621},"權限","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152838.png",[12,623,624],{},"打開產生的網址，把 Bot 加入你的伺服器。",[12,626,627],{},[15,628],{"alt":629,"src":630},"加入伺服器","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320153104.png",[12,632,633],{},[15,634],{"alt":629,"src":635},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320153150.png",[12,637,638],{},"接著回到 Claude Code，安裝 Discord Plugin：",[114,640,642],{"className":116,"code":641,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"\u002Fplugin install discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[73,643,644],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,645,646,648,650],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,647,203],{"class":129},[123,649,206],{"class":137},[123,651,652],{"class":137}," discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[19,654,655],{"title":21,"type":22},[12,656,214],{},[12,658,659],{},"安裝完之後，設定剛剛複製的 Token：",[114,661,663],{"className":116,"code":662,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"\u002Fdiscord:configure \u003Ctoken>\n",[73,664,665],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,666,667,670,672,674,676],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,668,669],{"class":129},"\u002Fdiscord:configure",[123,671,403],{"class":141},[123,673,406],{"class":137},[123,675,410],{"class":409},[123,677,413],{"class":141},[12,679,680,681,684,685,688],{},"跟 Telegram 一樣，Token 會被儲存在 ",[73,682,683],{},".claude\u002Fchannels\u002Fdiscord\u002F.env"," 中，你也可以用 ",[73,686,687],{},"DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN"," 環境變數來設定。",[12,690,691,692,227],{},"設定完退出 Claude Code，帶上 ",[73,693,226],{},[114,695,697],{"className":116,"code":696,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"claude --channels plugin:discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[73,698,699],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,700,701,703,705],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,702,237],{"class":129},[123,704,240],{"class":133},[123,706,707],{"class":137}," plugin:discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[12,709,710],{},"接著從你邀請 Bot 的 Discord 伺服器中，對 Bot 發送任何一段訊息，Bot 就會回覆你一組配對碼",[12,712,713],{},[15,714],{"alt":715,"src":716},"對話","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320153512.png",[12,718,719],{},[15,720],{"alt":715,"src":721},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320153652.png",[12,723,724],{},"回到 Claude Code 完成配對：",[114,726,728],{"className":116,"code":727,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"\u002Fdiscord:access pair \u003Ccode>\n",[73,729,730],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,731,732,735,737,739,741,743],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,733,734],{"class":129},"\u002Fdiscord:access",[123,736,479],{"class":137},[123,738,403],{"class":141},[123,740,484],{"class":137},[123,742,487],{"class":409},[123,744,413],{"class":141},[19,746,747],{"title":21,"type":22},[12,748,749,750,753,754],{},"這邊我有遇到一個狀況，就是配對碼一直過期，所以我改用 ",[73,751,752],{},"\u002Fdiscord:access allow \u003CsenderId>"," 直接把自己 Discord 的發送者 ID 加入白名單。如果你不知道該如何取得 Discord ID，你可以參考這篇文章：",[88,755,758],{"href":756,"rel":757},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20211013\u002F4225269670\u002F",[92],"一篇教你輕鬆取得自己的 Discord ID",[12,760,761],{},"然後一樣鎖定存取權限：",[114,763,765],{"className":116,"code":764,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"\u002Fdiscord:access policy allowlist\n",[73,766,767],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,768,769,771,773],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,770,734],{"class":129},[123,772,510],{"class":137},[123,774,513],{"class":137},[12,776,777],{},"這樣就完成啦～",[12,779,780,781,783],{},"當然，如果你想同時啟用多個 Channel 的話，可以在 ",[73,782,226],{}," 後面用空格分隔多個 Plugin，像是這樣：",[114,785,787],{"className":116,"code":786,"language":118,"meta":119,"style":119},"claude --channels plugin:telegram@claude-plugins-official plugin:discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[73,788,789],{"__ignoreMap":119},[123,790,791,793,795,798],{"class":125,"line":126},[123,792,237],{"class":129},[123,794,240],{"class":133},[123,796,797],{"class":137}," plugin:telegram@claude-plugins-official",[123,799,707],{"class":137},[27,801,803],{"id":802},"channels-的安全性","Channels 的安全性",[12,805,806],{},"你可能會擔心說 Channels 會不會有安全問題，這邊簡單說明一下好了。",[12,808,809],{},"其實每一個被核准的 Channel Plugin 都會維護一個發送者白名單（Allowlist），只有你手動加入白名單的 ID 才能推送訊息，其他人的訊息會被直接丟棄，所以不用太擔心有人亂發訊息來搗亂。",[12,811,812],{},"Telegram 和 Discord 都是透過配對碼機制來建立白名單的：",[814,815,816,819,822,825],"ol",{},[69,817,818],{},"在 Telegram 或 Discord 上對你的 Bot 發送任何訊息",[69,820,821],{},"Bot 回覆一組配對碼",[69,823,824],{},"在 Claude Code 中輸入配對碼來核准",[69,826,827],{},"你的發送者 ID 就會被加入白名單",[12,829,830,831,833,834,837,838,840],{},"除此之外，你還可以透過 ",[73,832,226],{}," 參數來控制每次 Session 要啟用哪些 Channel。就算一個 MCP Server 被寫在 ",[73,835,836],{},".mcp.json"," 中，如果沒有被加入 ",[73,839,226],{},"，它也沒辦法推送訊息進來。",[12,842,843],{},"所以整體來看，安全機制是多層防護的：Plugin 白名單 + 配對碼驗證 + Session 級別的啟用控制，用起來是不用太擔心的。",[27,845,847],{"id":846},"channels-vs-remote-control-vs-龍蝦openclaw","Channels vs Remote Control vs 龍蝦（OpenClaw）",[12,849,850],{},"看到這邊，你可能會好奇說 Channels 跟之前介紹過的 Remote Control 還有龍蝦有什麼不同，這邊簡單整理一下：",[852,853,854,873],"table",{},[855,856,857],"thead",{},[858,859,860,864,867,870],"tr",{},[861,862,863],"th",{},"項目",[861,865,866],{},"Channels",[861,868,869],{},"Remote Control",[861,871,872],{},"龍蝦（OpenClaw）",[874,875,876,891,905,917,930],"tbody",{},[858,877,878,882,885,888],{},[879,880,881],"td",{},"核心概念",[879,883,884],{},"外部事件推送到 Claude Code",[879,886,887],{},"手機\u002F瀏覽器直接操控 Claude Code",[879,889,890],{},"透過聊天平台操控電腦",[858,892,893,896,899,902],{},[879,894,895],{},"支援平台",[879,897,898],{},"Telegram、Discord（可擴充）",[879,900,901],{},"claude.ai\u002Fcode、Claude App",[879,903,904],{},"多種聊天平台",[858,906,907,910,913,915],{},[879,908,909],{},"雙向溝通",[879,911,912],{},"支援",[879,914,912],{},[879,916,912],{},[858,918,919,922,925,927],{},[879,920,921],{},"官方支援",[879,923,924],{},"Anthropic 官方",[879,926,924],{},[879,928,929],{},"第三方",[858,931,932,935,938,941],{},[879,933,934],{},"適用情境",[879,936,937],{},"想透過聊天平台推送事件或訊息",[879,939,940],{},"想直接操控 Claude Code Session",[879,942,943],{},"想用聊天平台操控整台電腦",[12,945,946],{},"簡單來講：",[66,948,949,954,959],{},[69,950,951,953],{},[187,952,869],{}," 適合你想要「直接操控」Claude Code Session 的情境，就像拿著遙控器一樣。",[69,955,956,958],{},[187,957,866],{}," 更偏向「事件驅動」，像是把 CI 結果、監控警報、聊天訊息推送進來，讓 Claude 自動處理。",[69,960,961,963],{},[187,962,872],{}," 則是第三方的方案，功能更泛用，但相對來講沒有官方的穩定性保障。",[27,965,966],{"id":966},"延伸閱讀",[12,968,969],{},"關於 Claude Code 生態系，這幾篇我之前寫過的也滿值得一讀：",[66,971,972,980,988],{},[69,973,974,979],{},[88,975,978],{"href":976,"rel":977},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fai\u002F20260128\u002F374686091\u002F",[92],"想用 Claude Code 開發？這篇帶你從入門到進階","：Claude Code 完整入門指南。",[69,981,982,987],{},[88,983,986],{"href":984,"rel":985},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fai\u002F20260319\u002F738324368\u002F",[92],"Claude Cowork Dispatch 與 Remote Control - 用手機遠端控制你的 AI Agent","：Channels 之外另一個官方的遠端方案。",[69,989,990,995],{},[88,991,994],{"href":992,"rel":993},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fgit\u002F20260121\u002F2025687513\u002F",[92],"Git Worktree 是什麼？一個專案同時跑多個 AI Agent 的秘訣","：搭配 Channels 並行任務的好搭檔。",[997,998,999],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .smYoP, html code.shiki .smYoP{--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-default:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark